{
  "stem": "3952.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was-- in Ebensee, they didn't-- they-- they could only burn 500 bodies a day, but there were more dead in a day than 500, so they stacked a huge room, five and five, five bodies over five bodies.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Five in length, five in large.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were some of them-- and he went into that room, and he took pictures.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He said some of them were still moving a leg or a hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Some of them were still saying, oy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he said, and this is only like five, six minutes walk from the tent where-- where I was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- and he said, Izchak, I cannot believe it's true.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because the human mind cannot accept.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In the same way, and I remember now, when I think of it, this is why we believed, no, it must have been a rag doll that they were throwing out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It must have not been a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It couldn't have been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Sure enough, it was a baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was young enough and had very good eyes-- at that time I was 17 years old-- to see 200 or 250 feet from me that it was a live baby that they throw out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I can't tell if it's a boy or a girl, but it was a live baby that they threw in the air, and four of them shot through that baby to see how many times they can shoot it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I think that's all I remember about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I don't even want to remember more, because it-- it-- it cost me-- it cost me too much to remember.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I would rather go back to where we were at the last--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like to go and tell that there were funny moments.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
